VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT \b(setuid|setgid|initgroups)\s*\(
WHEN EXPR MISSING:if\s*\(|==\s*-1|!=\s*0|perror|strerror|errno
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects the use of privilege-changing functions and ensures proper handling practices.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Insecure Handling of Privileged Operations.
